  <trk>
    <name>Around the Mattmark Reservoir in the Saastal</name>
    <desc>Pleasant route around the reservoir of Europe&apos;s largest earth dam framed by a dramatic mountain backdrop. The path along the west shore is accessible for wheelchairs and strollers.  </desc>
    <type>hikingTourTrail</type>
